# AI-Buzz Tools — Project Context

## Mission

Build free, genuinely useful tools for AI developers to validate demand, grow an email list, and help people. Not a startup (yet) — a portfolio of small bets to see what resonates.

## Success Metrics

- **Primary:** Someone reaches out saying "thank you" — proof of genuine utility
- **Secondary:** Email subscriber growth (target: 500 in 3 months)
- **Tertiary:** Organic search traffic to tools

## Constraints

- **Solo developer** — limited ongoing maintenance bandwidth
- **$0-20/month budget** — free tiers where possible (Render, Mailchimp)
- **Tools run themselves** — no manual maintenance required
- **No user accounts** — tools are free and anonymous

## Anti-Goals

- Don't build anything requiring ongoing manual maintenance
- Don't over-engineer before validation
- Don't add features unless they clearly help users make better decisions
- Don't let process slow down shipping

